## SubSection 2

- [**`test_objects`**](#var-test_objects): *(Optional `list(test_object)`)*<a name="var-test_objects"></a>

    - [**`nested_string`**](#attr-nested_string-2): *(Optional `string`)*<a name="attr-nested_string-2"></a>

      a nested string
